### âš™ï¸ **AdÄ±m 2: Django Backend API ve VeritabanÄ± ÅemasÄ±nÄ± HazÄ±rla**
LÃ¼tfen aÅŸaÄŸÄ±daki Django modellerini ve iliÅŸkileri oluÅŸtur:

```python
from django.db import models
from django.contrib.auth.models import AbstractUser

# KullanÄ±cÄ± Modeli
class User(AbstractUser):
    ROLE_CHOICES = [
        ('expert', 'Kalite UzmanÄ±'),
        ('agent', 'MÃ¼ÅŸteri Temsilcisi'),
        ('admin', 'YÃ¶netici')
    ]
    role = models.CharField(max_length=10, choices=ROLE_CHOICES)

# Ã‡aÄŸrÄ± KayÄ±tlarÄ±
class Call(models.Model):
    agent = models.ForeignKey(User, on_delete=models.CASCADE, related_name="calls")
    call_date = models.DateTimeField()
    phone_number = models.CharField(max_length=20)
    mp3_file = models.FileField(upload_to="call_records/")
    queue = models.CharField(max_length=50)

# DeÄŸerlendirme Formu
class Evaluation(models.Model):
    call = models.OneToOneField(Call, on_delete=models.CASCADE, related_name="evaluation")
    evaluator = models.ForeignKey(User, on_delete=models.CASCADE)
    scores = models.JSONField()  # PuanlarÄ±n JSON formatÄ±nda saklanmasÄ±
    comments = models.TextField()
    created_at = models.DateTimeField(auto_now_add=True)
